Shipboard oil pollution emergency plan
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 means a plan prepared, submitted, and maintained according to the provisions of &sect;&sect;151.26 through 151.28
of this subpart for United States ships or maintained according to the provisions of &sect;151.29(a) of this subpart
for foreign ships operated under the authority of a country that is party to MARPOL 73/78 while in the navigable waters
of the United States.
